hadiths[30]{hadithnumber,text}:
1175,"mainey ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey eik aisey shakhs key barey mein puchha jisney apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq dey di ho to unhoney kaha : kya tum Abdullah bin umr ko pehchantey ho? unhoney bhi apni biwi ko haiz ki haalat mein Talaq dey di thi, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha to aap ney unhen '' hukm diya ke wo usey ruju kar lein '' , Yunus bin Juber kehtey hain ke mainey puchha : kya ye Talaq shumar ki jaeygi ? kaha : to aur kya hogi ? ( yani kyon nahin shumar ki jaeygi ( , bhala bataao agar wo aajiz ho jata ya deewana ho jata to waqey hoti ya nahin?"
1176,"unhoney apni biwi ko haalat haiz mein Talaq dey di, unkey walid umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey masla puchha to aap ney farmaya : '' usey hukm do ke wo us sey ruju kar ley , phir tuhur ya hamal ki haalat mein Talaq dey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Yunus bin Juber ki hadees jisey wo ibne-Umar sey riwayat kartey hain, Hasan sahih hai. aur isi tarah Salim bin Abdullah ki bhi jisey wo ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat kartey hain, 2- ye hadees kaee aur turq sey bhi ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi hai aur wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke Talaq sunni ye hai ke aadmi tuhur ki haalat mein jima kiye baghair Talaq dey , 4- baaz kehtey hain ke agar usney tuhur ki haalat mein teen talaaqein din, to ye bhi Talaq sunni hogi . ye Shafai aur Ahmed bin Hanbal ka qol hai, 5- aur baaz kehtey hain ke teen Talaq talaq sunni nahin hogi , siwaye uskey ke wo eik eik Talaq alag alag kar key dey . ye Sufiyan Sory aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai, 6- aur ye log hamila key Talaq key barey mein kehtey hain ke wo usey jab chahey Talaq dey sakta hai, yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai, 7- aur baaz kehtey hain : usey bhi wo har maah eik Talaq dega ."
1177,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! mainey apni biwi ko qatae Talaq ( بتّہ ( di hai. aap ney farmaya : '' tum ney us sey kya murad li thi ? '' , mainey arz kya : eik Talaq murad li thi, aap ney puchha : '' Allah ki qism ? ''main ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! aap ney farmaya : '' to ye itni hi hai jitni ka tum ney irada kya tha ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko hum sirf isi tareeq sey jantey hain, 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : is mein iztirab hai, ikrima sey riwayat hai ke ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain Rukana ney apni biwi ko teen talaaqein di thin, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi hai ke unhoney Talaq bitta ko eik Talaq qarar di hai, 4- aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi hai unhoney usey teen Talaq qarar di hai, 5- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke is silsiley mein aadmi ki niyat ka aetbar hoga. agar usney eik ki niyat ki hai to eik hogi aur agar teen ki ki hai to teen hogi. aur agar usney do ki niyat ki hai to sirf eik shumar hogi. yehi Sory aur ehle-koofa ka qol hai, 6- Malik bin Anas qatae Talaq (bitta) key barey mein kehtey hain ke agar aurat aisi hai ke uskey sath dukhul ho chuka hai to Talaq bitta teen Talaq shumar hogi , 7- Shafai kehtey hain : agar usney eik ki niyat ki hai to eik hogi aur usey wapsi ka ikhtiyar hoga . agar do ki niyat ki hai to do hogi aur agar teen ki niyat ki hai to teen shumar hogi."
1178,"mainey Ayub ( sakhtiyaan ( sey puchha : kya aap Hasan Basri key ilawa kisi aisey shakhs ko jantey hain, jisney « أمرك بيدك » key silsiley mein kaha ho ke ye teen Talaq hai? unhoney kaha : Hasan Basri key . ilawa mujhey kisi aur ka ilm nahin, phir unhoney kaha : Allah ! maaf farmaai . haan wo riwayat hai jo mujh sey Qatada ney basanad « كثير مولى بني سمرة an أبي سلمة an أبي هريرة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم » riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aap ney farmaya : '' ye teen talaaqein hain ''. Ayub kehtey hain : phir main Kasir Mola bani Samra sey mila to mainey un sey is hadees key barey mein puchha magar wo usey nahin jaan sakey . phir main Qatada key paas aaya aur unhen ye baat batai to unhoney kaha : wo bhool gaey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Harab hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain unhoney usey Hammad bin Zaid sey riwayat kya hai, 3- mainey is hadees key barey mein Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey puchha to unhoney kaha : hum sey Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Harab ney bayan kya unhoney usey Hammad bin Zaid sey riwayat kya hai aur ye Abu-Hurera sey moqufan marvi hai, aur wo Abu-Hurera ki hadees ko marfoo nahin jaan sakey, 4- ehle-ilm ka « أمرك بيدك » key silsiley mein ikhtilaf hai, baaz Sahaba kiram waghaira jin mein umr bin Khattab , Abdullah bin Masood Raziallahu anhuma bhi hain kehtey hain ke ye eik ( Talaq ( hogi . aur yehi Tabe-een aur unkey baad key logon mein sey kaee ehle-ilm ka bhi qol hai, 5- Usman bin Affaan aur Zaid bin Sabit kehtey hain ke faisla wo hoga jo aurat kahegi , 6- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : jab shohar kahey ke '' uska maamla us ( aurat ( key haath mein hai'' , aur aurat khud sey teen Talaq qarar dey ley . aur shohar inkar karey aur kahey : mainey sirf eik Talaq key silsiley mein kaha tha ke uska maamla uskey haath mein hai to shohar sey qism li jaeygi aur shohar ka qol uski qism key sath moatabar hoga, 7- Sufiyan aur ehle-koofa umr aur Abdullah bin Masood Raziallahu anhuma key qol ki taraf gaey hain, 8- aur Malik bin Anas ka kehna hai ke faisla wo hoga jo aurat kahegi, yehi Ahmed ka bhi qol hai, 9- aur rahey Is-haq bin Raahviya to wo ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key qol ki taraf gaey hain."
1179,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamen ikhtiyar diya ( chahen to hum aap key nikah mein rahen aur chahen to na rahen ( hamney aap ko ikhtiyar kya. kya ye Talaq maana gaee thi ? padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ( sath rehney aur na rehney key ( ikhtiyar deney mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai. 3- umr aur Abdullah bin Masood Raziallahu anhuma ka kehna hai ke agar aurat ney khud ko ikhtiyar kar liya to talaq-baaina hogi . aur unhi dono ka ye qol bhi hai ke eik Talaq hogi aur usey wapasi ka ikhtiyar hoga . aur agar usney apney shohar hi ko ikhtiyar kya to is par kuch na hoga yani koi Talaq waqey na hogi, 4- aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke agar usney khud ko ikhtiyar kya to talaqe-baain hogi aur agar usney apney shohar ko ikhtiyar kya to eik hogi lekin wapasi ka ikhtiyar hoga, 5- Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke agar usney apney shohar ko ikhtiyar kya to eik hogi aur agar khud ko ikhtiyar kya to teen hongi , 6- Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad key logon mein sey aksar ehle-ilm o fiq'h is baab mein umr aur Abdullah bin Masood Raziallahu anhuma key qol ki taraf gaey hain aur yehi Sory aur ehle-koofa ka bhi qol hai, 7- albatta Ahmed bin Hanbal ka qol wohi hai jo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ka hai."
1180,"Fatima bint Qais (Raziallahu Anha) kehti hain ke mujhey merey shohar ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein teen talaaqein din padhi. to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tumhen na ( rihaaish ( milega aur na « nafqa » ( اخراجات ( ''. Mughira kehtey hain : phir mainey uska zikr Ibrahim Nakhai sey kya, to unhoney kaha ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka kehna hai ke hum eik aurat key kehney sey Allah ki kitab aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki sunnat ko tarak nahin kar saktey . hamen nahin malum ke usey ye baat yad bhi hai ya bhool gaee . umr aisi aurat ko «rihaaish» aur « nafqa » dilaatey they. dusri sanad sey Hushem kehtey hain ke hum sey Dawud ney bayan kya Shaaby kehtey hain : main Fatima bint Qais (Raziallahu Anha) key paas aaya aur mainey un sey unkey barey mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key faisley key mutalliq puchha to unhoney kaha : unkey shohar ney unhen Talaq bitta di to unhoney « rihaaish» aur « nafqa » key silsiley mein muqadma kya. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen na rihaaish hi dlwaya aur na « nafqa » . Dawud ki hadees mein ye bhi hai ke unhoney kaha : aur mujhey aap ney hukm diya ke main ibn Umme maktoom key ghar mein iddat guzaaron . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- baaz ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai. un mein Hasan Basri , Ata bin abi Ribah aur Shaaby bhi hain. aur yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain. un logon ka kehna hai ke mutallaqa key liye jab uska shohar wapasi ka ikhtiyar na rakhey na rihaaish hogi aur na nafqa , padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram mein sey baaz ehle-ilm jin mein umr aur Abdullah bin Masood Raziallahu anhuma hain kehtey hain ke teen Talaq wali aurat ko «rihaaish» aur « nafqa » dono milega . yehi Sory aur ehle-koofa ka bhi qol hai, 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : usey « rihaaish» milega « nafqa » nahin milega . ye Malik bin Anas , Les bin Saad aur Shafai ka qol hai, 5- Shafai kehtey hain ke hamney uskey liye «rihaaish» ka haq kitabullah ki buniyad par rakha hai, Allah Taala farmata hai : unhen unkey gharon sey na nikalo aur wo bhi na niklen siwaye uskey ke wo khullam khulla koi be-hayai kar bethein padhi. , « بذاء » ye hai ke aurat shohar key ghar walon key sath bad-kalami kerey. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Fatima bint Qais (Raziallahu Anha) ko « rihaaish » na deney ki illat bhi yehi hai ke wo ghar walon sey bad-kalami karti thin. aur Fatima bint Qais (Raziallahu Anha) key waqiey mein « nafqa » na deney ki Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadees ki ro sey usey nafqa nahin milega ."
1181,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ibne-Adam key liye aisi chiz mein nazar nahin jis ka wo ikhtiyar na rakhta ho, aur na usey aisey shakhs ko azad karney ka ikhtiyar hai jis ka wo Malik na ho, aur na usey aisi aurat ko Talaq deney ka haq hasil hai jiska wo Malik na ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , Muaz bin jabal, Jabir, ibne-Abbas aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. aur ye sab sey behtar hadees hai jo is baab mein riwayat ki gaee hai, 3- yehi Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka qol hai. aur Ali bin abi Talib , ibne-Abbas , Jabir bin Abdullah , Saeed bin Museiyab, Hasan , Saeed bin Juber , Ali bin Husein, Shureh , Jabir bin Zaid (Raziallauh anhum) , aur fuqaha Tabe-een mein sey bhi kaee logon sey yehi marvi hai. aur yehi Shafai ka bhi qol hai, 4- aur ibne-Masood sey marvi hai unhoney mansubey key silsiley mein kaha hai ke Talaq ho jaeygi, 5- aur ehle-ilm mein sey Ibrahim Nakhai aur Shaaby waghera sey marvi hai un logon ka kehna hai ke jab wo kisi waqt ki tehdeed karey padhi. to Talaq waqey ho jaeygi . aur yehi Sufiyan Sory aur Malik bin Anas ka bhi qol hai ke jab usney kisi mutayyan aurat ka naam liya , ya kisi waqt ki tahdeed ki ya yun kaha : agar mainey falan mahalley ki aurat sey shaadi ki to usey Talaq hai. to agar usney shaadi kar li to usey Talaq waqey ho jaeygi, 6- albatta ibne-Mubarak ney is baab mein shiddat sey kaam liya hai lekin unhoney ye bhi kaha ke agar usney aisa kya to main ye bhi nahin kehta ke wo is par haram hogi , 7- aur Ahmed kehtey hain : agar usney shaadi ki to main usey ye hukm nahin dunga ke wo apni biwi sey alehdgi ikhtiyar kar ley , 8- Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke main ibne-Masood ki hadees ki ru sey mansuba aurat sey nikah ki ijazat deta hun, agar usney us sey shaadi kar li , to main ye nahin kehta ke uski aurat is par haram hogi . aur ghair-mansuba aurat key silsiley mein Is-haq bin Raahviya ney wusat di hai, 9- aur Abdullah bin Mubarak sey manqul hai ke un sey eik shakhs key barey mein puchha gaya ke jisney Talaq ki qism khai ho ke wo shaadi nahin kerega, phir usey samajh mein aaya ke wo shaadi kar ley . to kya uskey liye rukhsat hai ke un fuqaha ka qol ikhtiyar karey jinhoney is silsiley mein rukhsat di hai? to Abdullah bin Mubarak ney kaha : agar wo us mamley mein padney sey pehley unkey rukhsat key qol ko durust samajhta ho to uskey liye unkey qol par amal durust hai aur agar wo pehley us qol sey mutmain na raha ho, ab aazmaaish mein pad janey par unkey qol par amal karna chahey to main uskey liye aisa karna durust nahin samajhta ."
1182,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' laundi key liye do hi Talaq hai aur uski iddat do haiz hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. hum isey Mazahir bin Aslam hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur Mazahir bin Aslam ki uskey ilawa koi aur riwayat merey ilm mein nahin, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. aur yehi Sufiyan Sory , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai."
1183,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala ney meri ummat key khayalat ko jo dil mein aatey hain maaf farma diya hai jab tak ke wo unhen zaban sey ada na karey , ya un par amal na karey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke aadmi jab apney dil mein Talaq ka khayal kar ley to kuch nahin hoga, jab tak ke wo munh sey na kahey."
1184,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' teen cheezen aisi hain ke unhen sanjeedagi sey karna bhi sanjeedagi hai aur hansi mazaq mein karna bhi sanjeedagi hai nikah, Talaq aur wapsi'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, 3- Abdur-Rehman, Habib bin Ardak madni key betey hain aur ibne-Maahik merey nazdik Yusuf bin maahik hain."
1185,"unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein Khulaa liya to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen hukm diya (ya unhen hukm diya gaya (ke wo eik haiz iddat guzaarein . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Rabee ki hadees ke unhen eik haiz iddat guzarney ka hukm diya gaya sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1186,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Khula leney wali aurten munafiq hain'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees us tareeq sey gharib hai, iski sanad qawi nahin hai, 2- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi hai aap ney farmaya : '' jis aurat ney bila kisi sabab key apney shohar sey Khula liya , to wo jannat ki khushbu nahin paeygi ''."
1187,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis aurat ney baghair kisi baat key apney shohar sey Talaq talab ki to is par jannat ki khushbu haram hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- aur ye « an أيوب an أبي قلابة an أبي أسماء an ثوبان » key tareeq sey bhi riwayat ki jati hai, 3- baaz ney Ayub sey isi sanad sey riwayat ki hai lekin unhoney usey marfoo nahin kya hai."
1188,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' aurat ki misal pasli ki hai padhi. agar tum usey sidha karney lagogey to tod dogey aur agar usey yun hi chhodey rakha to tedha key bawajud tum us sey lutf andoz hogey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai aur iski sanad jaiyed hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Zar , Samra , aur ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1189,"merey nikah main eik aurat thi, main us sey mohabbat karta tha, aur merey walid usey napasand kartey they. merey walid ney mujhey hukm diya ke main usey Talaq dey dun, lekin mainey un ki baat nahin maani. phir mainey uska zikr Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kya to aap ney farmaya : '' Abdullah bin umr ! tum apni biwi ko Talaq dey do''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, hum isey sirf ibne-Abi Zi-ib hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
1190,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aurat apni saukan ki Talaq ka mutalba na karey ke jo uskey bartan mein hai usey apney mein undel ley''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Umme-Salma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1191,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''har Talaq waqey hoti hai siwaye pagal aur deewaney ki Talaq key ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko hum sirf Ata bin Ajlan ki riwayat sey marfoo jantey hain aur Ata bin Ajlan zaeef aur « ذاہب الحدیث » ( hadees bhool janey waley ( hain, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke deewaney ki Talaq waqey nahin hoti siwaye uskey ke wo aisa deewana ho jiski deewangi kabhi kabhi theek ho jati ho aur wo ifaaqa ki haalat mein Talaq dey."
1192,"logon ka haal ye tha ke aadmi apni biwi ko jitni talaaqein deeni chahta dey dena ruju kar leney ki surat mein wo uski biwi bani rehti , agar-che usney soyaa us sey zayed baar usey Talaq di ho, yahan tak ke eik aadmi ney apni biwi sey kaha : Allah ki qism ! main tujhey na Talaq dunga ke to mujh sey juda ho jaey aur na tujhey kabhi panah hi dunga . usney kaha : ye kaisey ho sakta hai? usney kaha : main tujhey Talaq dunga phir jab iddat puri honey ko hogi to rujat kar lunga. us aurat ney Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key paas aa kar unhen ye baat batai to Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) khamosh rahIn, yahan tak ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aaye to Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney aap ko uski khabar di. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bhi khamosh rahey yahan tak ke Quran nazil huwa « الطلاق مرتان فإمساك بمعروف أو تسريح بإحسان » '' Talaq ( رجعی ( do hain, phir ya to maroof aur bhaley tareeqey sey rok lena hai ya bhalai sey rukhsat kar dena hai'' ( Baqra : ۲۲۹ ( . Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) kehti hain : to logon ney Talaq ko aainda naey sirey sey shumar karna shuru kya, jisney Talaq dey rakhi thi usney bhi, aur jisney nahin di thi usney bhi."
1193,"Sabiaa ney apney shohar ki maut key 23 ya 25 din baad bacha jana, aur jab wo nifaas sey pak ho gaee to nikah key liye zeenat karney lagi , is par aetraz kya gaya, aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey uska zikr kya gaya to aap ney farmaya : '' agar wo aisa karti hai) to harj ki baat nahin ( uski iddat puri ho chuki hai ''."
1194,"Abu-Hurera , ibne-Abbas aur abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman (Raziallauh anhum) ney aapas mein us hamila aurat ka zikr kya jis ka shohar faut ho chuka ho aur usney shohar ki wafat key baad bacha jana ho, ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ka kehna tha ke waza-hamal aur chaar maah das din mein sey jo muddat baad mein puri hogi uskey mutabiq wo iddat guzaaregi , aur abu-Salma ka kehna tha ke jab usney bacha jan diya to uski iddat puri ho gaee, is par Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main apney bhatijey yani abu-Salma key sath hun. phir un logon ney (eik shakhs ko) ummul-momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) key paas (masla malum karney key liye ( bheja , to unhoney kaha : sabeeaa Aslamiya ney apney shohar ki wafat key kuch hi dino baad bacha jana. phir usney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey (shaadi key silsiley mein) masla puchha to aap ney isey (nifaas ka khoon khatam hotey hi ( shaadi karney ki ijazat dey di . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1195,"Zenab bint abi Salma ney unhen ye teeno hadisein bataain ( un mein sey eik ye hai) Zenab kehti hain : main ummul-momenin Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu Anha) key paas aai jis waqt unkey walid abu-Sufiyaan sakhr bin Harab ka intiqal huwa , to unhoney khushbu mangaai jis mein khaluq ya kisi dusri chiz ki zardi thi, phir unhoney usey eik ladki ko lagaya phir apney dono rukhsaaron par lagaya , phir kaha : Allah ki qism ! mujhey khushbu ki zarurat nahin thi, lekin mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : Allah aur aakhirat par eman rakhney wali kisi aurat key liye jayez nahin hai ke kisi maiyat par teen din sey ziyada sog karey siwaye shohar key is par wo chaar maah das din tak sog kereygi."
1196,"Phir main Zainab binte Jahash (Raziallahu Anha) key paas aai jis waqt unkey bhai ka intiqal huwa to unhoney khushbu mangaai aur is mein sey lagaya phir kaha : Allah ki qism ! mujhey khushbu ki zarurat nahin thi, lekin mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : ''Allah aur aakhirat par eman rakhney wali aurat key liye jayez nahin hai ke kisi maiyat par teen raat sey ziyada sog kare siwaye apney shohar ke, wo is par chaar maah das din sog kareygi.''"
1197,"Mainey apni maa Ummul-momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) ko kehtey suna ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik aurat ney aa kar arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! meri beti ka shohar mar gaya hai, aur uski aankhen dukh rahi hain, kya hum us ko surma laga den? Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''nahin'. do ya teen martaba us aurat ney aap sey puchha aur aap ney har baar farmaya : ''nahin'' phir aap ney farmaya : ''(ab to Islam mein) iddat chaar maah das din hai, halanke jahiliyat main tum mein sey (faut shuda shohar wali bewa) aurat saal bhar ke baad oont ki mengni phainkti thi.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Zenab ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri ki behan Faiya binte Malik , aur Hafsa binte umr Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira ka isi par amal hai ke jis aurat ka shohar mar gaya ho wo apni iddat ke doran khushbu aur zeenat sey perhez kareygi. Sufiyan Sory , Malik bin Anas , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai."
1198,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us zihar padhi. karney waley key barey mein jo kaffare ki adaegi sey pehley mujaamiat (sambhog) kar leta hai farmaya : ''uskey ooper eik hi kaffara hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. Sufiyan , Shafai , Malik , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai. 3- aur baaz log kehtey hain ke agar kaffara ada karney sey pehley jimaa (sambhog) kar bethey to is par do kaffara hai. ye Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi ka qol hai."
1199,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik aadmi aaya , usney apni biwi sey zihar kar rakha tha aur phir uskey sath jimaa (sambhog) kar liya , usney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mainey apni biwi sey zihar kar rakha hai aur kaffara ada karney sey pehley mainey us sey jimaa (sambhog) kar liya to kya hukm hai? to aap ney farmaya : ''Allah tum par reham karey kis chiz ney tujh ko is par aamada kiya?'' usney kaha : mainey chaand ki roshni mein uski paazeb dekhi (tu mujh sey sabr na ho saka) aap ney farmaya : ''uskey qarib na jana jab tak ke usey kar na lena jiska Allah ney tumhen hukm diya hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
1200,"Salman bin Sakhr Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ney jo bani Biyaaza key eik fard hain apni biwi ko apney ooper mukammal maah Ramzan tak apni maa ki pusht ki tarah (haram) qarar dey liya. to jab aadha Ramzan guzar gaya to eik raat wo apni biwi sey jimaa (sambhog) kar bethey, phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye aur aap sey is ka zikr kiya, to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : ''tum eik ghulam azad karo'' unhoney kaha : mujhey ye muyassar nahin. aap ney farmaya : ''phir do maah key musalsal rozey rakho'' , unhoney kaha : main iski bhi istataat nahin rakhta to aap ney farmaya : ''saath miskeen ko khana khilaao'' , unhoney kaha : main iski bhi taqat nahin rakhta, to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Farwa bin Amr sey farmaya : ''usey ye khajuron ka tokraa dey do taake ye saath miskinon ko khila dey''  « arq » eik pemana hai jis mein pandarah saa ya sola saa ghalla aata hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Salman bin Sakhr ko Salma bin Sakhr Bayaazi bhi kaha jata hai. 3- zihar key kaffaarey key silsiley mein ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
1201,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apni biwiyon sey elaa padhi. kiya aur (un sey sohbat karna apney oopper) haram kar liya. phir aap ney haram ko halal kar liya aur qism ka kaffara ada kar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Muslima bin Alqama ki hadees ko jisey unhoney Dawud sey riwayat ki hai : Ali bin Mus'hir waghera ney bhi Dawud sey) riwayat ki hai magar ( Dawud ney Shaa'bi sey mursalan riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney elaa kiya. is mein Masruq aur Aaisha key wastey ka zikr nahin hai, aur ye Muslima bin Alqama ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Anas aur abu-Musa Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain. elaa ye hai ke aadmi chaar maah ya us sey ziyada dino tak apni biwi key qarib na janey ki qism kha ley. 3- jab chaar maah guzar jaeyn to is mein ulama ka ikhtilaf hai. Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke jab chaar maah guzar jaeyn to usey qazi key samney khada kiya jaeyga, ya to ruju kar ley ya Talaq dedey. 4- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein baaz ehle-ilm ka kehna hai ke jab chaar maah guzar jaeyn to eik Talaq baaen khud ba khud pad jati hai. Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-Koofa ka yehi qol hai."
1202,"Mus'ab bin Zuber ke zamanae-amaarat mein mujh sey liaan padhi. karney walon key barey mein puchha gaya ke kya unke darmiyan tafriq (farq) kar di jaey? to main nahin jaan saka ke main unhen kya jawab dun? chunanche main apni jagah sey uth kar Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma key ghar aaya aur andar aaney ki ijazat maangi , bataya gaya ke wo qailula kar rahey hain, lekin unhoney meri baat sun li , aur kaha : ibne Juber ! aa jaao tumhen koi zarurat hi ley kar aai hogi. Saeed bin Juber kehtey hain : main unkey paas gaya to kya dekhta hun ke paalaan par bichhaaey janey waley kambal par letey hain. mainey kaha : abu-Abdur-Rehman ! kya liaan karney walon key darmiyan tafriq kar di jaeygi ? kaha : Subhan Allah ! haan , sab sey pehley is barey mein falan bin falan ney poochha. wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya aur usney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! agar hum mein sey koi apni biwi ko burai kartey dekhey to kya kerey? agar kuchh kehta hai to badi baat kehta hai, aur agar khamosh rehta hai to wo sangeen maamla par khamosh rehta hai. ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khamosh rahey aur aap ney unhen koi jawab nahin diya. phir jab kuchh din guzrey to wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ( dobara ( aaya aur usney arz kiya : mainey aap sey jo masla puchha tha main is mein khud mubtala kar diya gaya hun. tab Allah Taala ney Sura : Noor ki ye aayaten nazil farmaeen :« والذين يرمون أزواجهم ولم يكن لهم شهداء إلا أنفسهم » ''yani jo log apni biwiyon par tohmat zina lagatey hain aur unkey paas khud apni zaat key ilawa koi gawah nahin hain'' (Sura Noor : 6). yahan tak ke ye aayaten khatam kin, phir aap ney us aadmi ko bulaya aur usey ye aayaten padh kar sunaaeyn, aur usey nasihat ki aur uski tazkeer ki aur bataya ke duniya ka azab aakhirat key azab sey aasan hai. is par usney kaha : nahin, us zaat ki qism ! jisney aap ko haq key sath bheja hai, mainey is par jhoota ilzam nahin lagaya hai. phir aap ney wo aayaten aurat key samney dohraaeen, us ko nasihat ki, aur uski tazkeer ki aur bataya ke duniya ka azab aakhirat key azab sey aasan hai. is par us aurat ney kaha : nahin, us zaat ki qism ! jisney aap ko haq key sath bheja , wo sach nahin bol raha hai. ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : aap ney mard sey ibtidaa ki, usney Allah ka naam ley kar chaar martaba gawahi di ke wo sacha hai aur paanchwen martaba gawahi di ke agar wo jhoota ho to is par Allah ki lanat ho. phir dobara aap ney aurat sey yehi baaten kahalwaaein, usney Allah ka naam ley kar chaar martaba gawahi di ke uska shohar jhoota hai, aur paanchwen martaba usney gawahi di ke agar uska shohar sacha ho to is par Allah ka ghazab nazil ho. phir aap ney un dono mein tafriq (farq) kar di. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Sehal bin Saad , ibne-Abbas , ibne-Masood aur Huzefa (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai."
1203,"Eik aadmi ney apni biwi key sath liaan kiya, to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un dono key darmiyan tafriq kar di aur ladkey ko maa key sath kar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
1204,"Fariaa bint Malik bin Sanan (Raziallahu Anha) jo abu Saeed Khudri ki behan hain ney unhen khabar di ke wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ayen , wo aap sey poochh rahi thin ke wo apney ghar walon key paas bani Khadra mein wapis chali jaeyn ( huwa ye tha ke) unkey shohar apney un ghulamon ko dhoondney key liye nikley they jo bhag gaey they, jab wo maqam qudoom key kinarey par un sey miley , to un ghulamon ney unhen maar dala . Fariaa kehti hain ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha ke main apney ghar walon key paas chali jaaun ? kyonkey merey shohar ney merey liye apni milkiyat ka na to koi makaan chhoda hai aur na kuch kharch to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' haan '', chunanche main wapis janey lagi yahan tak ke main hujra sharifa ya masjid nabawi hi mein abhi thi ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey aawaz di (ya aap ney hukm diya ke mujhey aawaz di jaey) phir aap ney puchha : ''tum ney kaisey kaha? mainey wohi qissa dohra diya jo mainey aap sey apney shohar key barey mein zikr kya tha, aap ney farmaya : ''tum apney ghar hi mein raho yahan tak ke tumhari iddat khatam ho jaey '', chunanche mainey usi ghar mein chaar maah das din iddat guzaari. phir jab Usman (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa huye to unhoney mujhey bulwaaya aur mujh sey us barey mein puchha to mainey unko bataya. chunanche unhoney uski perwi ki aur usi key mutabiq faisla kya. Muhammad bin Bashaar ki sanad sey bhi us jaisi usi mafhoom ki hadees aai hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka usi hadees par amal hai, ye log iddat guzarney wali aurat key liye durust nahin samajhtey hain ke apney shohar key ghar sey muntaqil ho jab tak ke wo apni iddat na guzar ley. yehi Sufiyan Sory , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai, 3- aur Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke agar aurat apney shohar key ghar mein iddat na guzaarey to us ko ikhtiyar hai jahan chahey iddat guzaarey, 4- (Imam Tirmizi ( kehtey hain : pehla qol ziyada sahih hai."
